Achievements.Name: Fashion Show
Achievements.Description: Unlock every character costume.

Achievements.Description: Unlock every Bestiary entry.

Achievements.Name: Maniac!
Achievements.Description: Kill 10,000 monsters.

Achievements.Name: Long, Hard Road Out Of Suburbia
Achievements.Description: Travel 1,000 kilometers

Achievements.Name: Archaeologist
Achievements.Description: Collect 72 Specialty Melee Weapons!

Achievements.Name: "It's Mine!  ALL MINE!"
Achievements.Description: Collect 10,000 Monster Tokens across all characters.

Achievements.Name: Trap Assassin
Achievements.Description: In Zack's House, use your cunning to defeat all of the enemies with traps! (on Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Name: Prowler On The Roof
Achievements.Description: Collect all weapon parts in Streets of Suburbia. (on Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Name: Did Someone Order Chinese?
Achievements.Description: Find a way to deal with that pesky Granny evil cat shield! (on Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Name: You Got Fur In The Hyperishdrive
Achievements.Description: Can you escape the garbage trucks of death without boosting? (on Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Name: Junkyards Just Aren't The Same
Achievements.Description: Make a mad dash to Bob Zombie! (on Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Name: I Said Turn Off Your Car Alarm!
Achievements.Description: Destroy all those pesky, loud cars in the Parking Lot with your mech! (on Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Description: These gold zombies trust you with their life. Show them you mean business. (on Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Description: Show the monster masses that vacuuming can be fun... by using excessive force! (Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Description: He's old and grumpy, so try to show him you care by not letting him get hurt. (Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Name: Very Sneaky, Sir
Achievements.Description: Show them you're a ninja of the night when taking back what's rightfully yours. (Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Description: Collect all weapon parts on Hell School Rooftops. (on Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Description: Let the monsters know that you're looking after their best gold interests. (Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Description: Resupplying is for the weak! Beat the final showdown without buying more ammo! (Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Description: Bring out the white knuckled driver in you and blast through the escape! (Thriller or higher)

Achievements.Name: A Little Help Goes A Long Way

Achievements.Name: Killing Machine!
Achievements.Description: Get 50% of the total kills in a ranked FFA Deathmatch game!

Achievements.Name: Control Freak
Achievements.Description: Perform all flag captures in a ranked CTF match!

Achievements.Name: Are You Crazy?!
Achievements.Description: Frag 4 players in under half a second in any ranked match!

Achievements.Name: Master Of Your Domain
Achievements.Description: Enter and never leave the hill in a ranked King of the Hill match!

Achievements.Description: Destroy the opposing team by having your team win with 100% of the kills in a ranked Team Deathmatch

Achievements.Description: Defeat all challengers using only your melee weapon in a ranked FFA Deathmatch!

Achievements.Name: You Deserve A Medal. A BIG One!

Achievements.Name: Block Party!

Achievements.Name: School's Out Foreva!

Achievements.Name: Graveyards Creep Me Out Too
Achievements.Description: Completed Chapter 4 Cemetary Scary.

Achievements.Name: Have Fun Stormin' the Castle!
Achievements.Description: Complete Chapter 5 Evil Castle.

Achievements.Name: A Hard Days Rockin
Achievements.Description: Play at least 24 hours of the single player adventure.

Achievements.Name: Homemade Weapon Club Card Holder
Achievements.Description: Attained all Level 1 weapons.

Achievements.Name: Homemade Weapon Club Chairman
Achievements.Description: Attained all Level 2 weapons.

Achievements.Name: Homemade Weapon Club Founder
Achievements.Description: Attained all Level 3 weapons.

Achievements.Name: Accessorize To The MAX!
Achievements.Description: Carried all secondary items at once.
